r all, while not being naive about it.");    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to West Freeport. Hand this note to Opal Darkbriar. She is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Grunson in East Freeport and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(18739);	quest::movepc(9,-710,138,17.7);  }  	if (($text=~/Innoruuk/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("Following the way of Innoruuk? A Good Choice, Followers of the Prince of hate believe hate is THE creative force of the universe.It isthe honest belief that if they hate strong enough they could destroy all of Norrath.");    quest::say("Very well, I  will send you to East Freeport Speak with Nexvok Thirod, she will guide your path.");	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Grunson in East Freeport and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(18854);	quest::movepc(10,-250,-38,-94.2);	}  if (($text=~/Karana/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("Following the way of The Karana? A Good Choice, Followers of The Rainkeeper believe in the absolute power of storms.");    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to South Qeynos. Hand this note to Gahlith Wrannstad, he is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Novalu and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(119875);	quest::movepc(1,-654,305,3.7);  }   if (($text=~/Mithaniel_Marr/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("Following the way of Innoruuk? A Good Choice, Followers of the Lightbringer belive that valor is what separates civilized beings from the beast. They have a strict moral code that prizes truth, honor and charity.");    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to West Freeport. Hand this note to Opal Darkbriar. She is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Grunson in East Freeport and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(18739);	quest::movepc(9,-710,138,17.7);	}	if (($text=~/Rodcet_Nife/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("Following the way of The Rodcet Nife? A Good Choice, Followers of The Prime Healer take oath to fight disease and death until one or the other takes them.");    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to South Qeynos. Hand this note to Gahlith Wrannstad, he is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Novalu and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(119875);	quest::movepc(1,-654,305,3.7);  }	if (($text=~/Solusek_Ro/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("Following the way of The Solusek Ro? A Good Choice, Followers of The Burning Prince in the raw and unbridled power of fire. Fire birthed the world andin fire shall it be consumed");    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to South Qeynos. Hand this note to Gahlith Wrannstad, he is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Novalu and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(119875);	quest::movepc(1,-654,305,3.7);	}  if (($text=~/West_Freeport/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to West Freeport. Hand this note to Opal Darkbriar. She is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Grunson in East Freeport and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(18739);	quest::movepc(9,-710,138,17.7);	}  if (($text=~/South_Qeynos/i) && ($ulevel == 1) && ($class eq "Wizard")) {    quest::say("On your way then, I will send you to South Qeynos. Hand this note to Gahlith Wrannstad, he is your Guildmaster of Enchanters."); 	quest::say("Be sure you find Soulbinder Novalu and have yourself bound to the area before you venture out. Good luck $name.");	quest::summonitem(119875);	quest::movepc(1,-654,305,3.7);	}}sub EVENT_ITEM {my $Wizard = quest::saylink("Wizard", 1);if (plugin::check_handin(\%itemcount, 18718 => 1) && $class eq "Wizard") {   quest::say("I am Gahlith Wrannstad of the Order of three. A few years ago, The Rathe server was created in order to bring back the feel of the orginal EQ zones. Many things have changed over the years and with those changes, some things could not be done anymore.");    quest::say("You were sent to me because there is a problem with getting you to the correct city with the correct guild summons.");	quest::say("Since you are talking to me I must assume you are a $Wizard?");	}if ($item1=="119875"){$client->Message(14,"Greetings $name, I am Gahlith, Master of the Wizard's Order of the Hall of Sorcery. Here, we have devoted our lives and souls to the study of the arcane. Study hard and master your skills, see Unsar Koldhagon, he will get you started.");quest::summonitem("13508");quest::ding();quest::faction(135, 10);quest::faction(240, 10);quest::faction(21, -30);quest::faction(235, -30);quest::exp("1000");}}#END of FILE Zone:qeynos ID:1064 -- Gahlith_Wrannstad
